41
00:02:24,084 --> 00:02:25,954
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>My old man...</i></b></font>

42
00:02:25,954 --> 00:02:30,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Unless I pass that car,</i>
<i>he won't admit that I won...</i></b></font>

43
00:02:32,064 --> 00:02:34,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>There's no other way...</i>
<i>I guess I have to do that...</i></b></font>

44
00:02:34,464 --> 00:02:37,404
