45
00:02:37,404 --> 00:02:41,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The setup point is in the next</i>
<i>five consecutive hairpin curves!</i></b></font>

46
00:02:42,404 --> 00:02:48,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Act 5: Dogfight!"</b></font>

47
00:03:06,394 --> 00:03:08,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Damn!</i></b></font>

48
00:03:15,534 --> 00:03:19,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>What's going on? Of all days,</i>
<i>today the FD feels extremely slow!</i></b></font>

49
00:03:19,874 --> 00:03:22,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Is the secondary turbine still working?</i></b></font>

50
00:03:57,044 --> 00:03:59,714
