Can you hear me?</b></font>

51
00:03:59,714 --> 00:04:01,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Ryosuke?</b></font>

52
00:04:01,354 --> 00:04:02,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Pretty soon,</b></font>

53
00:04:02,654 --> 00:04:05,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>the two will reach the five
consecutive hairpins up there.</b></font>

54
00:04:05,154 --> 00:04:06,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Give me the play-by-play.</b></font>

55
00:04:06,484 --> 00:04:09,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Tell me what's happening in
as much detail as possible.</b></font>

56
00:04:09,324 --> 00:04:11,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Okay. They're very close to us now.</b></font>

57
00:04:11,694 --> 00:04:15,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I can hear the sound of tires
squealing. They'll be here soon!</b></font>

58
00:04:15,994 --> 00:04:19,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Here they come!
Keisuke's FD! And the Eight-Six!</b></font>

59
00:04:19,334 --> 00:04:21,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They're neck and neck!</b></font>

60
00:04:27,714 --> 00:04:29,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Wow! Great! That Eight-Six is amazing!</b></font>

61
00:04:29,414 --> 00:04:31,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It did a perfect braking-drift!</b></font>

62
00:04:31,414 --> 00:04:33,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Keisuke is losing ground.</b></font>

63
00:04:35,184 --> 00:04:38,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>His recovery is great, too!
It's so close to the guardrail!</b></font>

64
00:04:38,254 --> 00:04:41,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They're going into the second
hairpin! There's no gap now!</b></font>

65
00:04:44,964 --> 00:04:47,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Recovery is the same for both of them!</b></font>

66
00:04:53,704 --> 00:04:57,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The FD got close to the outside!
The Eight-Six is...!</b></font>

67
00:04:57,044 --> 00:04:58,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The hairpin is coming!</i>
<i>But he's not slowing down!</i></b></font>

68
00:04:58,644 --> 00:05:00,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>What is he thinking?</i></b></font>

69
00:05:07,414 --> 00:05:11,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The Eight-Six is going into the
hairpin at an incredible speed!</b></font>

70
00:05:11,224 --> 00:05:13,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Are his brakes out?!</b></font>

71
00:05:16,494 --> 00:05:18,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What's that?!</b></font>

72
00:05:24,104 --> 00:05:28,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Keisuke was passed! Easily on the inside!</b></font>

73
00:05:32,704 --> 00:05:34,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That can't be true...</b></font>

74
00:05:34,344 --> 00:05:37,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We don't understand
what's happening! Be exact!</b></font>

75
00:05:37,414 --> 00:05:41,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But...we were watching it...</b></font>

76
00:05:41,414 --> 00:05:42,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...and a car shouldn't be able to turn</b></font>

77
00:05:42,854 --> 00:05:46,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>at a speed exceeding the tire's grip, right?</b></font>

78
00:05:46,024 --> 00:05:47,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But that Eight-Six turned in a weird way.</b></font>

79
00:05:47,854 --> 00:05:50,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It was kind of like a roller coaster,
even though that line was</b></font>

80
00:05:50,594 --> 00:05:52,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>supposed to be bad on the inside turn.</b></font>

81
00:05:52,864 --> 00:05:56,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I have no idea what happened!</b></font>

82
00:05:59,134 --> 00:06:02,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I know what the Eight-Six did.</b></font>

83
00:06:02,634 --> 00:06:04,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What?</b></font>

84
00:06:04,144 --> 00:06:08,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's a stupid thing, but no one can imitate it.</b></font>

85
00:06:08,644 --> 00:06:12,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>And it can happen only here on Akina.</b></font>

86
00:06:12,884 --> 00:06:16,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I can't believe anyone would
try something so stupid.</b></font>

87
00:06:17,224 --> 00:06:20,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I've got something to look forward to...</i></b></font>

88
00:06:20,024 --> 00:06:24,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Akina's downhill specialist...</i>
<i>You will be beaten by...</i></b></font>

89
00:06:24,164 --> 00:06:28,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>...me, Takeshi Nakazato of the Myogi Night Kids!</i></b></font>

90
00:06:32,204 --> 00:06:34,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This is the finish line! I can
hear the sound of their engines!</b></font>

91
00:06:34,774 --> 00:06:36,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They're almost here!</b></font>

92
00:06:37,744 --> 00:06:39,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Here they come! Which one's in the lead?!</b></font>

93
00:06:39,544 --> 00:06:40,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's the Eight-Six!</b></font>

94
00:06:40,774 --> 00:06:42,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Wow! What's going on?!</b></font>

95
00:06:42,774 --> 00:06:44,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Keisuke's FD is coming, too!</b></font>

96
00:06:44,244 --> 00:06:47,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But there is too much of
a gap for him to cover!</b></font>

97
00:06:47,084 --> 00:06:49,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The Eight-Six easily wins!</b></font>

98
00:06:52,554 --> 00:06:53,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Crap!</i></b></font>

99
00:06:53,854 --> 00:06:56,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>My FD beaten by an Eight-Six?!</i></b></font>

100
00:06:56,554 --> 00:06:58,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>That's impossible!</i></b></font>

101
00:06:58,694 --> 00:07:01,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>350 horses defeated by a shabby Eight-Six?!</i></b></font>

102
00:07:05,004 --> 00:07:06,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The Eight-Six just crossed the finish line!</b></font>

103
00:07:06,464 --> 00:07:08,134
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Keisuke has lost!</b></font>

104
00:07:08,134 --> 00:07:10,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We did it!</b></font>

105
00:07:28,724 --> 00:07:31,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Am I having a nightmare?</i></b></font>

106
00:07:31,194 --> 00:07:34,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I lost to an Eight-Six?! Twice?!</i></b></font>

107
00:07:37,734 --> 00:07:42,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Wow! He won! That spacey Takumi!</b></font>

108
00:07:42,004 --> 00:07:46,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Great! It's too cool! I'm totally numb.</b></font>

109
00:07:46,204 --> 00:07:49,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I feel like I'm going crazy.</b></font>

110
00:07:49,244 --> 00:07:51,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--He did it!
--Yeah!</b></font>

111
00:07:51,284 --> 00:07:53,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Iketani! Don't cry! You idiot!</b></font>

112
00:07:53,384 --> 00:07:56,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't know why... But I'm happy...</b></font>

113
00:07:56,354 --> 00:07:58,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Let's take lessons from him...</b></font>

114
00:07:58,884 --> 00:08:01,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Like drift control, and picking a line...</b></font>

115
00:08:01,994 --> 00:08:06,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Let's put the Speed Stars' sticker
on it without him knowing!</b></font>

116
00:08:06,294 --> 00:08:09,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Oh! I volunteer to do that! Iketani!</b></font>

117
00:08:09,464 --> 00:08:12,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>All right. I'll count on you...!</b></font>

118
00:08:12,804 --> 00:08:17,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It was a clear loss.
Let's admit it with some grace.</b></font>

119
00:08:17,674 --> 00:08:20,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>How about the timed run
for the uphill, Ryosuke?!</b></font>

120
00:08:20,644 --> 00:08:23,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The uphill doesn't mean anything.</b></font>

121
00:08:23,544 --> 00:08:27,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>By tomorrow, rumors will
spread among the street racers</b></font>

122
00:08:27,314 --> 00:08:33,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>that the undefeated Red Suns
lost to an Eight-Six from Akina...</b></font>

123
00:08:33,254 --> 00:08:35,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We will have to get even soon...</b></font>

124
00:08:35,994 --> 00:08:38,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...with my FC.</b></font>

125
00:09:51,404 --> 00:09:53,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A full tank of gas...</b></font>

126
00:09:53,264 --> 00:09:55,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's what you promised.</b></font>

127
00:09:56,504 --> 00:09:58,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You promised!</b></font>

128
00:10:03,674 --> 00:10:06,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I see... He won...</b></font>

129
00:10:06,014 --> 00:10:09,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I knew he would win even
before the race began...</b></font>

130
00:10:32,204 --> 00:10:37,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This right is where I was
passed by the Eight-Six.</b></font>

131
00:10:37,314 --> 00:10:39,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I just don't get it.</b></font>

132
00:10:39,384 --> 00:10:40,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>How could the Eight-Six,</b></font>

133
00:10:40,714 --> 00:10:44,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>which isn't good on inside corners,
go through it faster than my FD?</b></font>

134
00:10:44,454 --> 00:10:46,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Just remembering it gives me the creeps.</b></font>

135
00:10:46,754 --> 00:10:50,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He may be a real ghost...</b></font>

136
00:10:55,834 --> 00:10:57,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Keisuke...</b></font>

137
00:10:57,504 --> 00:10:59,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Tell me exactly what happened at that time.</b></font>

138
00:10:59,964 --> 00:11:03,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Was there anything strange?</b></font>

139
00:11:03,734 --> 00:11:07,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Come to think of it, I heard a
strange sound. Like scraping!</b></font>

140
00:11:07,674 --> 00:11:09,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A strange sound?</b></font>

141
00:11:12,914 --> 00:11:14,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I see... Now I understand.</b></font>

142
00:11:14,554 --> 00:11:16,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What?</b></font>

143
00:11:16,054 --> 00:11:20,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Should I tell you why you lost?</b></font>

144
00:11:35,574 --> 00:11:39,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He used this.</b></font>

145
00:11:39,744 --> 00:11:43,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--A drainage ditch?
--Yes.</b></font>

146
00:11:43,044 --> 00:11:45,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He dropped his inside tires
into the ditch on purpose</b></font>

147
00:11:45,614 --> 00:11:49,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and resisted the centrifugal
force by hooking it.</b></font>

148
00:11:49,384 --> 00:11:51,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>In that way, it is theoretically possible to gain</b></font>

149
00:11:51,584 --> 00:11:55,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>more cornering force than the tires can grip.</b></font>

150
00:11:57,294 --> 00:12:01,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It is too obvious and simple,
and it's a ridiculous idea.</b></font>

151
00:12:01,734 --> 00:12:05,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It wouldn't be successful
if he'd never done it before.</b></font>

152
00:12:05,864 --> 00:12:10,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I assume that he probably
practices like this regularly.</b></font>

153
00:12:10,434 --> 00:12:13,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He must have run Akina for many years.</b></font>

154
00:12:15,044 --> 00:12:16,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Damn!</b></font>

155
00:12:16,674 --> 00:12:18,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The mountain downhill is fun</b></font>

156
00:12:18,884 --> 00:12:20,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>because this kind of thing happens.</b></font>

157
00:12:20,854 --> 00:12:21,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's been a while</b></font>

158
00:12:21,884 --> 00:12:26,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>since I've met a target that
I can get excited about.</b></font>

159
00:12:27,724 --> 00:12:31,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Let's cancel the expedition
we were planning for next week.</b></font>

160
00:12:31,524 --> 00:12:35,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Until we have a complete victory
at Akina, we can't move on.</b></font>

161
00:12:35,694 --> 00:12:38,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll beat the Eight-Six!</b></font>

162
00:12:44,474 --> 00:12:47,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Green Shopping Street"</b></font>

163
00:12:53,744 --> 00:12:56,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Bunta! Are you in?!</b></font>

164
00:12:54,914 --> 00:12:57,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Closed Today"</b></font>

165
00:12:56,254 --> 00:12:57,954
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's me!</b></font>

166
00:12:57,954 --> 00:12:59,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Oh, it's hot.</b></font>

167
00:12:59,424 --> 00:13:01,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Oh, it's Yuichi...</b></font>

168
00:13:01,594 --> 00:13:03,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Good timing!</b></font>

169
00:13:03,354 --> 00:13:06,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I have a meeting at the Chamber of Commerce.</b></font>

170
00:13:06,194 --> 00:13:08,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Sorry to bother you,
but can you give me a ride?</b></font>

171
00:13:08,534 --> 00:13:12,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What? Are you using me as a taxi?</b></font>

172
00:13:17,034 --> 00:13:20,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I heard Takumi was great...</b></font>

173
00:13:20,444 --> 00:13:23,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Iketani and the others have been
excited about it all morning.</b></font>

174
00:13:23,774 --> 00:13:26,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's not particularly great.</b></font>

175
00:13:26,044 --> 00:13:30,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I've heard that the expectations
of kids these days are pretty low.</b></font>

176
00:13:30,354 --> 00:13:33,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He doesn't like driving cars.</b></font>

177
00:13:33,554 --> 00:13:36,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Is that right? I can't believe it.</b></font>

178
00:13:36,754 --> 00:13:39,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He has such a great technique.</b></font>

179
00:13:39,224 --> 00:13:44,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>To him, driving a car equals
helping with my business.</b></font>

180
00:13:44,364 --> 00:13:47,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I've forced him to do it
since he was in junior high,</b></font>

181
00:13:47,364 --> 00:13:50,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>so he can't imagine that driving is fun.</b></font>

182
00:13:50,734 --> 00:13:52,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I see...</b></font>

183
00:13:52,404 --> 00:13:56,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He's somewhat cynical about it.</b></font>

184
00:13:56,744 --> 00:14:00,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But the chase on the
downhill of Akina last night</b></font>

185
00:14:00,444 --> 00:14:04,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>might have given him
something to feel passionate about.</b></font>

186
00:14:05,884 --> 00:14:08,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Speaking of which, I didn't see the Eight-Six...</b></font>

187
00:14:08,494 --> 00:14:10,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Where is Takumi?</b></font>

188
00:14:10,254 --> 00:14:11,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't know what's going on,</b></font>

189
00:14:11,924 --> 00:14:15,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but he went somewhere
this morning in a good mood.</b></font>

190
00:15:01,974 --> 00:15:03,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Fujiwara Tofu Shop"</b></font>

191
00:15:13,054 --> 00:15:15,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Wow! It's cold!</b></font>

192
00:15:17,524 --> 00:15:20,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi, you're...</b></font>

193
00:15:20,164 --> 00:15:23,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...a very good driver.</b></font>

194
00:15:23,864 --> 00:15:25,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Really?</b></font>

195
00:15:25,604 --> 00:15:29,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>To tell you the truth, I usually get carsick.</b></font>

196
00:15:29,834 --> 00:15:33,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>So I brought medicine for it.</b></font>

197
00:15:33,104 --> 00:15:37,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But I didn't feel sick at all
when you were driving.</b></font>

198
00:15:37,684 --> 00:15:39,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This is the first time I didn't get sick</b></font>

199
00:15:39,944 --> 00:15:42,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>after being in the car for so long.</b></font>

200
00:15:44,384 --> 00:15:47,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Do you ride in cars that often?</b></font>

201
00:15:47,724 --> 00:15:51,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Oh... not that often...</b></font>

202
00:15:51,264 --> 00:15:56,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Just when my family goes
out and my father drives...</b></font>

203
00:15:58,234 --> 00:16:01,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>She is strange...</i></b></font>

204
00:16:01,004 --> 00:16:04,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I was just driving like I usually do</i></b></font>

205
00:16:04,574 --> 00:16:07,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>so I don't spill the water in the paper cup.</i></b></font>

206
00:16:13,344 --> 00:16:16,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>It was strange yesterday...</i></b></font>

207
00:16:16,014 --> 00:16:19,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The car running in front of me</i>
<i>was getting closer and closer,</i></b></font>

208
00:16:19,024 --> 00:16:21,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>and the next thing I knew...</i></b></font>

209
00:16:21,654 --> 00:16:24,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>...I found myself getting a</i>
<i>charge out of chasing it.</i></b></font>

210
00:16:45,214 --> 00:16:51,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I've never thought driving was fun before...</i></b></font>

211
00:16:51,084 --> 00:16:54,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Even today, when I was</i>
<i>driving with Mogi next to me,</i></b></font>

212
00:16:54,694 --> 00:16:57,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>it was a lot of fun.</i></b></font>

213
00:16:57,764 --> 00:17:00,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Driving isn't that bad...</i></b></font>

214
00:17:02,534 --> 00:17:04,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey, Takumi.</b></font>

215
00:17:04,464 --> 00:17:07,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey! Hello!</b></font>

216
00:17:07,834 --> 00:17:10,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You were daydreaming just now.</b></font>

217
00:17:10,474 --> 00:17:12,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Were you spacing out?</b></font>

218
00:17:12,904 --> 00:17:16,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're rude, Takumi.</b></font>

219
00:17:16,044 --> 00:17:18,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>When a person has a cute girl with him,</b></font>

220
00:17:18,344 --> 00:17:21,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>do you think he should be off
in his own little world? Really!</b></font>

221
00:17:21,984 --> 00:17:24,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Sorry! What did you say?</b></font>

222
00:17:24,884 --> 00:17:28,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I just asked if you have a girl you like.</b></font>

223
00:17:31,564 --> 00:17:35,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't have anyone in particular...</b></font>

224
00:17:37,194 --> 00:17:40,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Although I do have someone I
can't help thinking of a little...</b></font>

225
00:17:42,204 --> 00:17:44,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>How about you?</b></font>

226
00:17:44,504 --> 00:17:47,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I also have...</b></font>

227
00:17:47,204 --> 00:17:50,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...someone I can't help thinking of a little.</b></font>

228
00:17:56,714 --> 00:17:59,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What are you saying? Don't be a copycat.</b></font>

229
00:18:02,124 --> 00:18:03,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Boy!</b></font>

230
00:18:03,324 --> 00:18:05,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't know how many times</b></font>

231
00:18:05,564 --> 00:18:08,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I was asked the same thing this morning.</b></font>

232
00:18:08,864 --> 00:18:11,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>"Who was in that Eight-Six yesterday?"</b></font>

233
00:18:11,504 --> 00:18:13,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I was asked many times, too.</b></font>

234
00:18:13,804 --> 00:18:16,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Anyway, he beat Keisuke Takahashi.</b></font>

235
00:18:16,904 --> 00:18:20,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's no surprise that people are talking.</b></font>

236
00:18:20,174 --> 00:18:22,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I got a little carried away...</b></font>

237
00:18:22,174 --> 00:18:25,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I told everyone that the Eight-Six was</b></font>

238
00:18:25,184 --> 00:18:27,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>the secret weapon of the Speed Stars.</b></font>

239
00:18:27,344 --> 00:18:30,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We have to find a way to get
Takumi to join the Speed Stars.</b></font>

240
00:18:30,184 --> 00:18:32,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Otherwise, we'll be embarrassed later.</b></font>

241
00:18:32,054 --> 00:18:35,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Iketani! Leave it to me!</b></font>

242
00:18:35,354 --> 00:18:39,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Because I'm his best friend,</b></font>

243
00:18:39,024 --> 00:18:40,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll make him do it.</b></font>

244
00:18:40,824 --> 00:18:42,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Are you sure, Itsuki?</b></font>

245
00:18:42,564 --> 00:18:44,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Of course!</b></font>

246
00:18:44,364 --> 00:18:47,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I know his weak points, too...</b></font>

247
00:18:49,334 --> 00:18:53,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But in return, please let
me join the Speed Stars!</b></font>

248
00:18:53,244 --> 00:18:57,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If Takumi will join us, you're in. Right?</b></font>

249
00:18:57,374 --> 00:18:59,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah...</b></font>

250
00:19:00,614 --> 00:19:02,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Lucky! The negotiation was successful!</b></font>

251
00:19:02,814 --> 00:19:05,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But how are you going to get a car?</b></font>

252
00:19:05,654 --> 00:19:07,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm glad you asked!</b></font>

253
00:19:07,654 --> 00:19:09,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I've already made up my mind!</b></font>

254
00:19:09,654 --> 00:19:11,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Oh! You've finally saved up the money!</b></font>

255
00:19:11,794 --> 00:19:17,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll ask my dad to sign for me
and get a loan for an Eight-Six!</b></font>

256
00:19:17,564 --> 00:19:19,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi has a Panda Trueno,</b></font>

257
00:19:19,304 --> 00:19:22,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>so I'll look for a red or black Levin...</b></font>

258
00:19:22,004 --> 00:19:25,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...and someday we'll be
called the Eight-Six Pair,</b></font>

259
00:19:25,044 --> 00:19:27,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>the fastest in Akina.</b></font>

260
00:19:31,914 --> 00:19:33,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But, Itsuki...</b></font>

261
00:19:33,684 --> 00:19:37,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...Takumi's Eight-Six is not a normal Eight-Six.</b></font>

262
00:19:37,484 --> 00:19:38,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's right.</b></font>

263
00:19:38,724 --> 00:19:43,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It was faster than the FD
with 350 horsepower...</b></font>

264
00:19:43,594 --> 00:19:46,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It must have incredible tuning.</b></font>

265
00:19:46,824 --> 00:19:50,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'd like to take a peek under the hood.</b></font>

266
00:19:50,834 --> 00:19:55,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Instead of that, why don't you go along</b></font>

267
00:19:55,274 --> 00:19:59,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>when he goes for Akina's downhill record?</b></font>

268
00:19:59,244 --> 00:20:01,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Wow! That's a good idea!</b></font>

269
00:20:01,214 --> 00:20:03,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I want to ride, too!</b></font>

270
00:20:03,214 --> 00:20:06,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We can go where no one has gone before!</b></font>

271
00:20:06,944 --> 00:20:10,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--I can't even imagine it...
--Yeah...</b></font>

272
00:20:10,014 --> 00:20:14,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I bet it's greater than any
extreme roller coaster.</b></font>

273
00:20:14,554 --> 00:20:17,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah...</b></font>

274
00:20:17,394 --> 00:20:21,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Crap! Right now, Takumi is...!</b></font>

275
00:20:32,574 --> 00:20:35,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Beach House"</b></font>

276
00:20:37,984 --> 00:20:40,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Wait a minute! Takumi!</b></font>

277
00:20:45,984 --> 00:20:48,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Excuse me! Could you take our picture?</b></font>

278
00:20:48,294 --> 00:20:49,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>All right.</b></font>

279
00:20:51,464 --> 00:20:54,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What's this? We're going to take a photo?</b></font>

280
00:20:54,064 --> 00:20:56,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We came all this way. It's for our memories.</b></font>

281
00:20:56,964 --> 00:20:59,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Smile! Smile!</b></font>

282
00:20:59,004 --> 00:21:00,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Here we go.</b></font>

283
00:21:02,704 --> 00:21:05,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Excuse me! One more!
Please take one more picture!</b></font>

284
00:21:05,844 --> 00:21:07,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's enough...</b></font>

285
00:21:07,204 --> 00:21:09,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Never mind, never mind!</b></font>

286
00:21:33,034 --> 00:21:35,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Oh! That white FC!</b></font>

287
00:21:35,474 --> 00:21:37,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's Ryosuke Takahashi.</b></font>

288
00:21:37,534 --> 00:21:40,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Finally, Red Suns' No. 1 showed up!</b></font>

289
00:21:40,644 --> 00:21:42,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What for?</b></font>

290
00:21:42,744 --> 00:21:45,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Must be revenge for his brother.</b></font>

291
00:21:45,144 --> 00:21:47,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Can you think of anything else?</b></font>

292
00:21:47,114 --> 00:21:49,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That was just yesterday!
He came here already?!</b></font>

293
00:21:49,714 --> 00:21:53,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He must be really mad about being
beaten by the Eight-Six. I wonder...</b></font>

294
00:21:55,654 --> 00:21:58,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's an R32 I've never seen here.</b></font>

295
00:21:59,764 --> 00:22:01,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A black R32...</b></font>

296
00:22:01,224 --> 00:22:04,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Something about it makes me shiver...</b></font>

297
00:22:04,334 --> 00:22:06,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Who is that?</b></font>

298
00:22:43,774 --> 00:22:46,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>My pride says you gotta be wild and tough</i></b></font>

299
00:22:46,474 --> 00:22:48,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>So no one intervenes</i></b></font>

300
00:22:48,544 --> 00:22:50,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Never stop, I don't want to stop</i></b></font>

301
00:22:50,074 --> 00:22:52,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Even if you cry because of a sacrificed love</i></b></font>

302
00:22:52,144 --> 00:22:53,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Aim for the peak, sweep the winding street</i></b></font>

303
00:22:53,944 --> 00:22:56,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Beep beep! The warning chime is so cheap!</i></b></font>

304
00:22:56,154 --> 00:22:57,614
